title: Dhol
subTitle: Four lazy friends want to make easy money and aim to marry a rich girl. Their plan backfires after they meet Ritu and get embroiled with a dangerous criminal.

title: Saajan
subTitle: Breaking conventional barriers, a poor, disabled orphan befriends the son of a wealthy businessman. However, their friendship is put to the test after both friends fall in love with the same woman.

title: Bal Ganesh 3
subTitle: Dhoti, Topi and Suit Boot are more than happy to oblige when a group of alien kids come over to listen to adventure stories about their favourite Bal Ganesh.

title: Maine Dil Tujhko Diya
subTitle: Ajay falls in love with Ayesha, a fellow college student who is the daughter of a rich businessman. However, problems arise when Ayesha's father arranges her marriage to an associate's son.

title: Jaisi Karni Waisi Bharni
subTitle: A conniving son throws his aged parents out of the house. Years later, he meets the same fate when his son decides to teach him a lesson.

title: Dil
subTitle: A father pretends to be a rich industrialist to improve his son's chances of marrying in to wealth. However, his plan backfires on him when his true identity is found out.

title: Vishwatma
subTitle: A policeman and a reformed criminal go to Kenya to comprehend a syndicate leader. However, they must break the rules of the land defended by Surya Pratap, a Kenyan police inspector.

title: Ziddi
subTitle: Deva, a vigilant young man, quickly climbs amongst the ranks of criminals in his city. However, things get complicated when he is framed for the assassination attempt of the CM.

title: Izzatdaar
subTitle: When Brahm Dutt, a wealthy businessman, is falsely convicted on murder charges, he enlists the help of a boy to exact revenge on Indrajeet, his cruel son-in-law and the cause of all his miseries.

title: Izzatdaar
subTitle: When Brahm Dutt, a wealthy businessman, is falsely convicted on murder charges, he enlists the help of a boy to exact revenge on Indrajeet, his cruel son-in-law and the cause of all his miseries.

title: Mashaal
subTitle: After being dismissed from his job as a newspaper editor, Vinod Kumar relocates to the slums of Bombay and starts his own publication.

title: Masoom
subTitle: D K Malhotra leads a peaceful life with his wife and two daughters. But all of this changes when he is forced to bring a boy, who is his son from a previous relationship, home after his mother dies.

title: Tumko Na Bhool Payenge
subTitle: Veer, a villager, becomes restless after he is haunted by the visions of his past. When he is attacked on the day of his wedding, he forces his parents to reveal the truth about his identity.

title: Hum Hai Rahi Pyar Ke
subTitle: Rahul looks after his spoilt nephews, Sunny and Vicky, and niece, Munni. When they go to a funfair, they meet Vyjayanti, who has run away from home, and decide to shelter her without Rahul's consent.

title: Mehndi
subTitle: Newly-wed Pooja is left shocked when her in-laws and her husband start ill-treating her. Unable to bear the mistreatment, she decides to teach them a lesson.

title: Raghuveer
subTitle: Ravi, an honest policeman, leads the bodyguard team of the chief minister. When his college-going brother, Raghuveer, is arrested and jailed, Ravi breaks all ties with him out of embarrassment.

title: Tridev
subTitle: When an expelled police inspector, an outlaw and a commissioner's son are implicated by a dealer, they unite to seek revenge and prove they are not culprits.

title: Kahin Pyar Na Ho Jaye
subTitle: Prem's heart fills with despair when the woman he loves fails to show up for their wedding day. However, his life soon takes an unexpected turn with the arrival of a new neighbour.

title: Kahin Pyar Na Ho Jaye
subTitle: Prem's heart fills with despair when the woman he loves fails to show up for their wedding day. However, his life soon takes an unexpected turn with the arrival of a new neighbour.

title: Hera Pheri
subTitle: Vijay and Ajay make a living by stealing money from people. Their friendship is affected when Vijay discovers that Ajay's father may have been his father's killer.

title: Bhoothnath Returns
subTitle: After returning to Earth to scare children, the ghost Bhoothnath befriends Akhrot and helps him earn money. Unexpectedly, they take on the country's most powerful politician.

title: Student of the Year 2
subTitle: Rohan follows his lover, Mridula, to St Teresa's college hoping to reunite with her. There, he befriends Manav, the most popular student, but is constantly at loggerheads with his sister, Shreya.

title: Bandhan
subTitle: Thakur marries his mistress when his first wife, Pooja, is unable to bear children. His brother-in-law opposes this marriage to save the dignity of his sister and fights to reunite them.

title: Rakshak
subTitle: ASP Raj Sinha is assigned to catch the criminal responsible for printing and circulating fake currency notes. However, he is shocked to learn that the person is none other than his childhood friend.

title: Dil Pardesi Ho Gayaa
subTitle: When Major Ram of the Indian Army is captured by the Pakistani military, his younger brother Sunny begins a daring mission to rescue him, only to find himself falling for a Pakistani woman.

title: Border
subTitle: A small battalion of Indian soldiers go up against a 2000 well-armed Pakistani strike force. They must defend their post all night until they receive assistance from the Indian Air Force.

title: Farishtay
subTitle: Veeru and Dheeru live under the tyrant ruler, Raja Jaichand. Later, they embark on a mission and strive to overcome challenges to defeat the dictator.
